      "title": "[DC] ice3564@🔸guides: For those who still have no clue about team setup with Saya.  I have test her wi",
      "summary": "For those who still have no clue about team setup with Saya. \nI have test her with potential gameplay change and here are the result from my testing.\nI have provide replay code of some awakener that their gameplay or damage output have change drastically bcuz of Saya.\n\n1. Saya best pairing with Thais for consistent embryo regen and debuff.\n\n2. Then you might need to have 1 card searcher/drawer, such as Ramona, Ryker, Faros, depend on your team line up.\n\n3. as far as I have test, the main dmg dealer that perform amazingly with Saya are;\n\n**Chaos**\n- Mouchette\n- Kath\n- 24Caro  - a bit underwhelm, but with Saya corrosion she can do decent amount of damage and bleed\n24 replay - __c5464efa-1173-3c9c-bc00-f745b7619364#E#a__\n\n**Caro** ( Don't you dare ask about Doresain, he is beyond saving)\n- Sorel (she was mid, but now she is so good with Saya)\nSorel replay - __577451ee-1196-3dbf-8c27-8de18adeb23a#E#a__\n\n- Thais Dmg dealer built\n\n**Aequor**\n- Gmurphy\n- Vortice ( her gameplay with Saya will blow your mind, with proper team setup you can OE her every turn) \nVortice replay - __f09f9e11-7410-3c2e-aecd-a31f87e76106#E#a__\n\n- Sanga ( not crazy dmg but HUGE shield every turn)\nSanga replay - __bddf4861-3f2e-3fb0-ad08-e78c3f98ee69#E#a__\n\n- Corposant\n\nUltra \nI did not have a proper ultra unit built so I dont want to test it.\n\nPS. If you want any character to be tested with Saya or replay, feel free to let me know.\nPS2.  I will do in-depth video about Saya gameplay and her setup. but will take sometime for that.",
